  "3093020": {
    "name": "Circle Empires 2",
    "steam_appid": 3093020,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《环形帝国》归来！没错，我们又回到了最初的圆环之地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个由无数环形大陆拼接而成的世界里，你将征服强敌、掠夺宝藏、壮大军势，同时顺应环形世界的不断变化，打造独一无二的游戏体验。招募属于你的独特兵种组合，在<strong>《环形帝国2》</strong>中驰骋战场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新兵种、武器与玩法模式登场，你可以和好友并肩作战，也能独闯荣耀征途。无论你是初入帝国的新手，还是纵横沙场的老将，圆环之战将永无止息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>环环相扣的世界 《环形帝国2》</strong>的帝国由无数圆环构成！每个圆环都是独立的小生态圈，遍布资源、野兽与敌人。夺下圆环便能赢得先机，但要小心：每个圆环都潜藏新的威胁，阴险强敌与残暴首领无处不在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/dbab5a6da82ff7338ba31263395cf1df.poster.avif?t=1771250037\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/dbab5a6da82ff7338ba31263395cf1df.webm?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/dbab5a6da82ff7338ba31263395cf1df.mp4?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>兵种百态，战术无限 </strong>指挥千军万马，每个兵种都有独特技能。从勇猛的战士、隐秘的弓手，到驾驭野兽的法师——合理搭配才是制胜之道。借助<strong>全新的“兵种自定义”系统</strong>，打造你的专属战队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/96a135b9ec20731ae0336fbfbe4a1c46.poster.avif?t=1771250037\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/96a135b9ec20731ae0336fbfbe4a1c46.webm?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/96a135b9ec20731ae0336fbfbe4a1c46.mp4?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>局局不同，永不重复 </strong>每次开局，都是全新的冒险！随机地图与圆环带来无限战术可能，无论是深思熟虑的智者，还是敢拼敢闯的勇士，都能在<strong>《环形帝国2》</strong>的不同难度等级下尽情享受游戏乐趣。游戏设置每日任务和排行榜，等你来一决高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/bde319f7dd1634bdc7d628fc974251db.poster.avif?t=1771250037\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/bde319f7dd1634bdc7d628fc974251db.webm?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/bde319f7dd1634bdc7d628fc974251db.mp4?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>好友同乐，乐趣加倍 </strong>征服之路若能与朋友同行，乐趣自然翻倍！在多人模式中，你可以与盟友携手征服世界，也可以各自为战，一较高下。友情与火力齐飞，战斗更为酣畅！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/3d489dc7839347ef370fff4ef565fabe.poster.avif?t=1771250037\" width=600 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/3d489dc7839347ef370fff4ef565fabe.webm?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093020/extras/3d489dc7839347ef370fff4ef565fabe.mp4?t=1771250037\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色一览：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快节奏即时战略：</strong>建造、扩张、征战，环环紧扣！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无限可重玩性：</strong>随机生成的地图、生物与敌人，每局都是全新体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样兵种与成长：</strong>从弓手到死灵法师，升级进化，驾驭更强大的战斗坐骑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>骑乘系统：</strong>创造性组合兵种，小兵骑乘巨兽，战场奇招百出。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更强的敌人：</strong>敌人将使用更高明的战术，你必须不断调整应对。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人模式：</strong>和朋友合作或对抗，征服更精彩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态环境：</strong>探索多样地貌，化环境为武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富自定义：</strong>自由调整设定与难度，打造专属战场体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全新内容：</strong>新增兵种、建筑、地形效果与升级系统，让策略更具深度。</p></li></ul>",
